## Output Format

Please output only valid JSON, with no explanations or markdown code blocks.

{
  "hook": "The eye-catching text shown or spoken in the first 3 seconds of the video; recommended 8–15 characters",
  "duration_seconds": {{ duration_seconds }},
  "shots": [
    {
      "time_range": "0-5s",
      "visual": "Visual description: what is shown, how it cuts, whether there is a text overlay",
      "subtitle": "Subtitle copy for this 5-second segment",
      "mood": "steady / passionate / warm / tense / relaxed"
    }
  ],
  "title_options": [
    "Title option 1",
    "Title option 2",
    "Title option 3"
  ],
  "music_mood": "calm | uplifting | corporate"
}

Requirements:
- Total shots: 3–8, each 5–15 seconds
- Subtitle copy should be conversational and match the speaker's style
- Do not output anything the speaker would not say
- duration_seconds must be an integer between 15 and 60
- Output JSON only
